Twitter Client [TEST]

Features:
 - User autentification without using any browser (via WebView)
 - Remember last signed username for future easier autentification
 - Dispaly user`s home timeline
 - Update status
 - Search tweets
 - Pretty scroll to refresh list view by both ways(up - down) from Chris Banes
 - Images` caching for the better performance
 - Small optional menu to switch off or exit from app with following preferences cleaning and process killing
 
 Usage:
 Just implement these two projects and emulate/upload it to your phone to see an effect.
 
 Problems:
 If you have any errors with attached library, may be, you just need to reconfigure Pull-To-Refresh library path.